Interface ReaderDeviceSerializer

All Known Implementing Classes:
ReaderDeviceSerializerImpl, ReaderDeviceSerializerImpl
public interface ReaderDeviceSerializer

ReaderDeviceSerializer objects serialize a command on a ReaderDevice into a String representation.
